# Ontology header
#######################################################################

<https://github.com/RubenZoodsma/Alarm-Ontologie/ontology/instances/alarm-condition-descriptions>
    a owl:Ontology ;
    rdfs:label "Alarm Condition Descriptions (ACD)" ;
    rdfs:comment "Defines AlertConditionDescription instances with explicit semantic requirements for alarm activation" .

##### Initially included alarms: 
